owl:Ontology.terms:creator: Georg Ferdinand Schneider
owl:Ontology.terms:description:
This ontology aims at modelling the semantics of the basic data types provided by the XSD standard for OWL ontologies. In particular, it provides the possibility to describe basic data types as resources rather then RDF Literals.
This problem appears to be existent also in other domains such as e-commerce, e.g. https://www.w3.org/2011/webschema/track/issues/14
